OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome evening sunshine to start with,
OL,7,Fbut low cloud and mist gradually
OL,8,Freturning from the coast. Cloud
OL,9,Fspreading further south and west
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FMainly dry on Saturday but
OL,13,Frather cloudy with the odd spot of
OL,14,Frain possible in the morning. A much
OL,15,Fcooler day than Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
